content: Bit tired today. been working on so many differnet project, yet unable to get any to work the way i would like
feedback: It's wonderful that you've taken the first step in your mental wellness journey by starting this journaling practice. It sounds like you're juggling quite a bit, and it's understandable to feel tired when things aren't going as planned. This might be a good opportunity to explore perfectionist thinking patterns, where we set very high standards for ourselves and feel disappointed when things don’t meet them. Consider using the "thought record" technique to identify and reframe these thoughts, or try setting smaller, achievable goals to build a sense of accomplishment. Keep up the great work with your journaling—each entry is a step toward greater self-awareness and growth.
